<plot>Joe McDoakes (George O'Hanlon)is invited by his boss to a swanky dance. Joe admits he can't dance and the boss gives him a lesson in the office. At the dance, Joe is a social failure and makes many mistakes while dancing with his boss' wife. Joe goes to a dancing school and becomes a big success.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?503882</url></doc>
